{"tid":1647581,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[小心入][劇透] El Camino: A Breaking Bad Movie 《續命之徒》觀後感","createTime":"2019-10-11T21:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T19:01:26.000Z","uid":313640,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"08845b839a206f1c221a2b8ff3e166794dbba561","tid":1647581,"uid":313640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:31:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><ins><strong>深夜讀後感</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n幾個鐘前睇完,見到其他Post同埋網上嘅影評好多都係話套戲係幫Jesse寫埋個結尾,其實講真認為今次套戲無動搖到<span style=\"color: green;\">Breaking Bad</span>喺我心目中嘅神劇地位,反而仲有小小圓滿嘅感覺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kTfxEYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkTfxEYs.jpg&h=585b8a1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基本劇情就係<span style=\"color: blue;\">Jesse</span>比<span style=\"color: blue;\">Mr. White</span>釋放咗之後，決定搵吸塵機鋪老闆幫佢&quot;消失&quot;，途中有些少阻滯,最後搞掂,重頭嚟過,完。<br />\n<br />\n巴打你無睇錯,個故事就係咁簡單,但就啱啱好完到我地fans嘅心願,亦即係<span style=\"color: blue;\">Jesse Pinkman</span> 嘅結局。<br />\n<br />\n細節嚟講,<span style=\"color: blue;\">mike,Todd,jane,</span>同埋<span style=\"color: blue;\">Mr. White</span> 嘅出現當然係唔少得嘅fan service,同時間佢地每一個都有出現嘅原因同意義,豐富咗成個故仔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3TbVBs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3TbVBs.jpg&h=b57847a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Mike</span>同<span style=\"color: blue;\">Jesse</span>嘅對話,講要<span style=\"color: red;\">start over</span>,係成套戲嘅序曲,而<span style=\"color: blue;\">Jesse</span>講到<span style=\"color: red;\">想彌補自己犯事過嘅所有錯誤,</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"> mike</span>就答佢<span style=\"color: red;\">咁係無可能嘅</span>。<span style=\"color: blue;\">Mike</span>喺劇入面殺人無數,佢嘅罪固然唔使多講,而Jesse 嘅經歷,佢所犯嘅每一個錯誤,都令到佢愛嘅人同佢自己承受好慘痛嘅後果,<span style=\"color: blue;\">Jesse</span>係鋪頭同吸塵機佬講&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">你想像唔到我有幾咁後悔當日無上你㗎車走!</span>&quot;睇得出Jesse比人捉住嗰陣,係受盡<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">身心嘅折磨</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXrtdj0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXrtdj0.jpg&h=2a96d615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺劇入面,<span style=\"color: orange;\">Todd</span>一直都比<span style=\"color: blue;\">Jesse</span>一種好似對佢好好,會幫佢講說話嘅好人形象,但事實上同佢uncle一樣都係咁變態。係套戲入面都一樣見到<span style=\"color: orange;\">Todd</span>係一個冷血,心理變態嘅人,一路話個清潔呀姨好人,一路叫<span style=\"color: blue;\">jesse</span>埋咗佢條屍,用條皮帶勒死人之後仲要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">面不改容拎返嚟帶</span>,可以話係更加解釋到<span style=\"color: blue;\">Jesse</span>當時點解要親手解決<span style=\"color: orange;\">Todd</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yCNstUW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyCNstUW.jpg&h=37d68ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而<span style=\"color: blue;\">Walter White</span>喺最後嘅登場,係場戲入面見到當時嘅<span style=\"color: blue;\">Jesse</span>仲係一個會為自己搵到嘅錢而興奮嘅古惑仔,仲會關心<span style=\"color: blue;\">Mr. White</span>嘅病嘅一個學生,而<span style=\"color: blue;\">walter</span>就仍然係嗰個為屋企人而製毒,仲會關心<span style=\"color: blue;\">Jesse</span>未來嘅化學老師,同佢地之後嘅心態同境況相比,係更加沉淪,同埋不受控制。係咁大嘅對比之下,可以睇到兩個角色嘅深入描寫影響到幾咁大嘅故事深度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxqd8Ut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuxqd8Ut.jpg&h=ef9cb7a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫面方面，維持住Breaking Bad嘅一貫風格，係鏡頭角度同剪接上落足心機，遠鏡嘅沙漠、用俯憾嘅角度影住<span style=\"color: blue;\">Jesse</span>搜索間屋,影住成間房嘅間隔並帶嚟一種壓迫感,flash back同現實故事嘅剪接過鏡都非常出色。(下面張GIF係套劇唔係套戲)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TmaxE2c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTmaxE2c.gif&h=9a32db0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而彩蛋就當然大把啦,有一個比較明顯嘅就係,喺兩個假差佬搜緊todd間屋嗰陣,搵到一個水晶球上面有todd同埋坐係個杯上面嘅Lydia,係一個劇入面todd鍾意Lydia嘅Refrence。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DujKv5T.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDujKv5T.gif&h=ba331551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後總括返,<span style=\"color: blue;\">Jesse</span>最後，向佢屋企人承認返自己嘅錯，成功逃走左之後嗰個笑容釋放返佢受咁多年壓力嘅內心，為<span style=\"color: green;\">Breaking Bad</span>畫上左一個完美句號。"},{"pid":"a8ef76723e6b7662e6bf0d4396fc4b7a75bd3975","tid":1647581,"uid":196445,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:35:46.000Z","msg":"喊咗，尤其是Mr. White出場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d044732857ef29311fcff04b449ac026a22b13a","tid":1647581,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:44:36.000Z","msg":"netlifx有冇得睇"},{"pid":"76f316e7858329715ab94e6dfe587fe8c1c9c35b","tid":1647581,"uid":6239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d044732857ef29311fcff04b449ac026a22b13a","tid":1647581,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:44:36.000Z","msg":"netlifx有冇得睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:45:44.000Z","msg":"緊係有"},{"pid":"0cc8596839f0183df201bb292500379435ef5005","tid":1647581,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76f316e7858329715ab94e6dfe587fe8c1c9c35b","tid":1647581,"uid":6239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d044732857ef29311fcff04b449ac026a22b13a","tid":1647581,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:44:36.000Z","msg":"netlifx有冇得睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:45:44.000Z","msg":"緊係有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb019f2057612fee537140cf4071d8e6148940f","tid":1647581,"uid":196445,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T21:58:54.000Z","msg":"我都想去阿拉斯加，脫離一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089b6f947d5665a5891f57032e81b22394a234b9","tid":1647581,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T23:09:11.000Z","msg":"其實我唔明嘅係點解jesse做人地便宜老豆會做到咁上心,係因為佢愛屋及烏定係因為佢欠咗個𡃁仔(害到佢無咗兄弟同老母)?<br />\n<br />\n始終佢兄弟都係殺咗佢個friend,又係因為自己捲入去佢地到先搞到條女死埋<br />\n<br />\n劇入面唔上&quot;重新做人貨van&quot;係因為